{"tid":809964,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企隻狗好唔聽教","createTime":"2018-09-07T14:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T00:48:53.000Z","uid":205491,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a09ccc082c2f141f80dce539a50dabb9b201d3b1","tid":809964,"uid":205491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T14:48:18.000Z","msg":"屋企隻狗8個月大（tiny)女仔黎，成日亂咬同食屋企啲家私、報紙、膠袋、牆，基本上咩都會咬同食。<br />\n（我懷疑佢唔識分咩係食物，因為我比藥佢佢都食得好開心）<br />\n已經將啲野放到好高同收埋曬，但家私呢啲就真係無辨法。（我有買玩具比佢玩同咬）<br />\n佢好中意入同咬梳化底，成個底比佢咬爛曬，仲吞左好多材料入肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最近仲咬到去木個層，吞左啲木，搞到佢嘔返曬啲糧仲有啲血絲，第日即刻帶佢睇醫生，好彩冇事，冇整親啲腸。<br />\n佢係知我唔比佢入個底到，已經睇實佢，但有時去一去洗手間，食緊野，睇少一眼就即刻入左去。<br />\n以前我淨係捉住佢罵，依加我罵完會困佢入籠，<br />\n但都係唔得，隻狗只要一冇人睇住就會唔自律。<br />\n仲成日挑戰我，愈唔比佢做o既野愈要做。<br />\n點先可以教好隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/224612_aad13c26e5a8e10f31d6f11632d57c97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F224612_aad13c26e5a8e10f31d6f11632d57c97.png&h=6a8a83fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0697737d7688dca953d02033d8bb65dc1707569e","tid":809964,"uid":207443,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"一路睇落去一路諗<br />\n點解甘似我之前隻poodle 甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再睇埋落去見到幅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係笑鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f28220d871b3b13000c42cb232fbfcebdffcf6","tid":809964,"uid":142518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T14:53:09.000Z","msg":"買隻公狗返嚟教訓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbf65818367f276e604e0f1493fdc8e79a3baee","tid":809964,"uid":187116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T14:55:37.000Z","msg":"笑左<br />\n隻狗同樓主鬥智"},{"pid":"9e4257cd1cdb7cb2f533c6ab712e1a792ed0ed1d","tid":809964,"uid":205474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e81f70eec0b0293079fb8036d056f01743d0c14a","tid":809964,"uid":155067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:14:50.000Z","msg":"大d會好d,適當體罰對狗係work"},{"pid":"171cac2317cba634e347078fa24f5a04b8187ff1","tid":809964,"uid":205491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e81f70eec0b0293079fb8036d056f01743d0c14a","tid":809964,"uid":155067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:14:50.000Z","msg":"大d會好d,適當體罰對狗係work"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"我隻狗係唔驚體罰，例如佢係到咬張凳，我會彈佢個嘴，之後怒啤我再咬，好似啲死o靚仔，愈唔比佢做愈要做，佢係知我唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a855d1d28d65b3edc4a276e555a1efbd32dd054","tid":809964,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:47:10.000Z","msg":"狗種問題，呢種狗本身真係比較唔聽教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8785e3cdbd16a75c9886e0d396a67ed0843f8305","tid":809964,"uid":80576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"感覺係佢未知邊個係主人 所以根本唔驚"},{"pid":"277fbe5d7eeff29762526c136b28579324220cff","tid":809964,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36280d629cce5bd9086c890e0c8008e6aef5fdd9","tid":809964,"uid":121087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:00:36.000